&\frac{4x-x^3}{(x+2)(x-1)}\\

& = \frac{-x(x^2 -4)}{(x+2)(x-1)}\\

&= \frac{-x(x+2)(x-2)}{(x+2)(x-1)} \\

&= \frac{-x(x-2)}{x-1}

\end{aligned}

